title: Newstralia (Innovation)
description:
Uncle Ichthy returns to the land of Innovation Comics with "Newstralia"!

Newstralia was a five-issue series published by Innovation somewhat haphazardly in 1989-90. It was created by Stephen Sullivan and Tim Truman, with Truman providing the covers (along with the layouts for #1). According to the cover blurb:

'NEWSTRALIA is a tale of rebellion and deceit in the far future. It is also the name of a new supercontinent, a hostile world filled with famine, mutants, and the malevolent Iron Church -- and three unlikely heroes. Their plan? Survival.'

Multiple thanks to the creative teams and the scanners! Get it, seed it!
